This Book Library Management System includes:

## Features Implemented:

### Authentication & Authorization
- User registration and login with email/password
- Role-based access control (Admin/User)
- Protected routes based on user roles
- Session management with NextAuth.js

### Admin Functionality
- Add new books with title, author, genre, and total copies
- View all books with availability status
- Edit and delete book records
- Track borrowed vs available copies

### User Functionality
- Browse available books catalog
- Borrow books (if copies available)
- Return borrowed books
- View personal borrowed books list with borrow dates
- Prevent duplicate borrowing of same book

### Database Schema
- Users table with role management
- Books table with inventory tracking
- Borrows table for lending history
- Proper relationships and constraints

### Technical Features
- Responsive design with Tailwind CSS
- Server-side rendering with Next.js App Router
- Form validation and error handling
- Real-time availability tracking
- Clean, organized code structure

